This paper discusses cyber attacks and their impact on organizations, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also touches on the need for organizations to defend against such attacks, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE) or cyber physical systems (cs.CY). The paper also discusses the details of specific cyber attacks, which could fall under the categories of security and privacy (cs.SI) or cryptography and security (cs.CC).
